{"lemma":"أَحَمَّيْ","slug":"أَحَمَّيْ","root":"ح.م.م","root_slug":"ح-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9218"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"black"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Color or defect adjective from the root ح م م (ḥ m m).\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9218","headword_ar":"احمى","root":"HmY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, in five places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"the sun, and fire,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be vehemently hot;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of God: (Lh, K:) and in like manner, a piece of iron; said of a man: (Msb:) [or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he heated"},{"kind":"text","text":"an iron nail, (ISk, K,) and a piece of iron, (ISk, S,) &c., in the fire: (ISk:) one should not say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaY","text_ar":"حَمَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sense; (ISk, S, Msb, TA;) app., in chaste speech; for otherwise one does say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaY Al$~aYo'a fiY Aln~aAri","text_ar":"حَمَى الشَّىْءَ فِى النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the thing into the thing into the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so heated it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmY Almiysama","text_ar":"احمى المِيسَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmY Ealayohi","text_ar":"احمى عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He kindled fire upon the branding-iron"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so heated it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmAhu EalaY AlqitaAli","text_ar":"احماهُ عَلَى القِتَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He excited him to ardour for fight"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HrD","text_ar":"حرض"},{"kind":"text","text":"; &c.)"}],"source_refs":["Lh","K","Msb","ISk","S"]}]}}